ays,\u8232 though as a warrior I once excelled.\u8232 But come, you must continue with these games\u8232 to honour your companion. As for this gift,\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0800\u8232 I accept it gladly. It delights my heart\u8232 that you think of me always as your friend.\u8232 You don\'92t forget the honours due to me\u8232 among Achaeans. May the gods grant you,\u8232 as a reward for that, your heart\'92s desires.\'94\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0[650]\
